2009-03-19  karl <charcoal@users.sf.net>

	* enable InvStrongsRealGreek lemma lookup when "stype" is not
	  present.  bad side effect is that we don't handle Hebrew lemmas,
	  but right now there are no Hebrew modules with lemmas, so, eh. :-)
	  this lookup is imprecise due to InvStrongsRealGreek being
	  imprecisely ordered, consequent to diacriticals not sorting well.

