2007-08-22  karl <charcoal@users.sf.net>

	* integrate cygwin strcasestr() from 2.2.
	* use correct #ifndef for gtkhtml/gecko in find_dialog.c.
	* incorporate an img src prefix fix from 2.2.
	* attempt to generalize to gtkhtml3 the "big blob" gecko fix of
	  SysTheo, so as to address e.g. ISBE "genealogy" (96kbyte entry) --
	  seems to be a bug in recent pango; cygwin was already fine with it.

